Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is today the last day of Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have lots of cute cosplay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Okarin's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we weren't doing the cracking, and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's gonna reach a high of 35!{35°C = 95°F}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying hydrated is the best way to prevent heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to Comima today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really sunny out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each D-mail I undid delayed Mayuri's death by one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erasing Suzuha's D-mail made the events of the 13th occur on the 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Faris, Rukako, Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If each one pushed it back a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then in this world line, Mayuri will die on the 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, before 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I got one for Daru too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there was a book on a robot anime I thought you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if there's anywhere you'd like to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to think about, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Organization assassins hiding in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do something to escape their clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not careful, they might find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the original plan until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think any bad people like that are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet back here at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're selling juice over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before then, I'll have to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a way for her to survive without changing world lines.
