Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to help Hashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A notepad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A list of circles at Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The rack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at the second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously having you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You stopped it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so we haven't touched it for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain what's going on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri will die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you're doing the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To erase the first D-mail you sent—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think of a way to save Mayuri without the cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have changed. This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I won't be able to think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have time for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hide things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want to stop by the lab, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii was thinking of getting some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}almost time for her to die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely went to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to check something out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've shown you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many things Mayushii knows more than Okarin about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never gone to Comima together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so Mayushii was happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see Rukako looking embarrassed in cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if he had, he would've been really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Ruka would've gotten his photo on all the blogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would've become a worldwide superstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Mayushii would've seen it and said, "He's come a long way."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I could really see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be even better if Okarin cosplayed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange, you'd have to do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call Rukako and Cristina,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can convince them to do it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do that, then I,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma the mad scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,shall make my cosplay debut at Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kurisu was interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so Mayushii will try her best to do it by the next Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The next...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My watch isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wound—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stop it from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I let that car hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}something has to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... Finally, I was useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii was useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see the stars from here, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\move(1066,523,915,523,0,2460)\frz339.8}I want to talk to you. \NKurisu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start the cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've been on the roof for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without so much as a peep, so I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought the FBI would come, and you got scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to be thought of as a law-abiding citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your normal hotshot attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The great mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I act like that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew within five seconds of meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you time leap again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've helped you with everything so far, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it this far by thinking things through together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha and Faris...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed the things they wanted the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, this is how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe, you were crying back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida was worried too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought maybe you had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,July 28th...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri and I went to Doctor Nakabachi's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I saw Makise Kurisu collapsed after being stabbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know by whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a text to Daru's cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which was connected to the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The first D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the message that moved us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Beta world line to the Alpha world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Deleting that message from SERN's database
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and returning to the Beta world line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,means going back to that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we return to the Beta world line...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If we undo that first D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daru told me you were acting odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii's been so busy with Comima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that she couldn't spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you used to talk to Mayushii about all kinds of stuff, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There were four Organization generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Geppu, Sudachi, Seiyuu, and Jakkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu, Suzaku, Seiryuu, and Byakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked hearing about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mayushii is ever a burden, you'd tell me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mayushii can do anything for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,call me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From your voice, I can guess what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go see her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to come up with any answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you stay here to talk to with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you were sitting here alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you should go see Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll only hurt my pride if you stay here and worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mayushii. I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the cosplayers said Mayushii left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to see me because it's Obon, right, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been having scary dreams lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the dreams, terrible things happen to Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets shot with a pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or she's in a car accident or run over by a train,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything seems like it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary, and it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to scream for help as loud as I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of the dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin always comes to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii says, "Thank you, Okarin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He holds Mayushii, and he looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He never cries, but you can tell he really wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mayushii says,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but he doesn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk about something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, there have been a lot of new lab members!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Kurisu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Moeka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka, and Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, it was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu is super smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and she talks about all these really hard things with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin looks happy now that he gets to talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, sometimes I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time Mayushii went to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the beginning of spring, but it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to the lab after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was cleaning up the room, he came in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, "Welcome back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't say, "I'm back."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Good work."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, every day after that, I'd go there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for about two hours, and we would barely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't bad. We were simply there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passed so slowly, and it was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii thought she really was like a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing good happened, but it was good anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You saw some kind of illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may be an attack by Organization General Illusion Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I bet that Illusion Contactor—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think he's a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't spent much time talking with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be that, when I saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell he's really suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,like he's always about to cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know he's thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a burden to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about something sad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mayushii's been lonely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always know where my hostage is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Hououin Kyouma,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,am not so weak that I need you to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get another Upa toy, right?
